text: Ariane Rump is a German water polo player. She was part of the German women's national water polo team at the 2003 World Aquatics Championships, and 2007 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * FINA world championship Ariane Rump * Ariane Rump Getty Category:German water polo players Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people
